reviewText: It is great and I love it.
This movie is hilarious. I am so glad I took the chance on a "previously viewed" DVD.
This is a really fun movie.  It's very busy and never a dull moment.  Also teaches about taking chances to better your life and not living in fear of change.  Sometimes CHANGE is good!

I watch this movie with my 2 year old about 5 times a day. I cannot say no when she grabs my face and says "Guy Guy Guy?" She loves this movie, and I enjoy it also even having to watch it 5 times a day.
We love this movie and watch it often. It is clean and really funny! It is the only movie my husband can watch more than once and my kids love it.

Regardless of what other individuals have said -pro or con about this movie -- I sure liked it after it got a bit into it. At first, living in a cave didn't do much for me, but as the movie progressed it became Funny in enough places to have made the purchase worthwhile. At least from my view point, the more I watch it the more I'll enjoy it, and I believe that You Will Too, even though it's different.
